1. *Pomozi* mi i ja ću pomoći tebi. (Help me and I will help you.)
2. Ona je prethodno *pomogla* nam mnogo. (She had previously helped us a lot.)
3. *Pomogao* sam im da pronađu svoj put. (I helped them to find their way.)
4. Ona je sada u problemu i treba nam da *pomognemo* joj. (She is now in trouble and we need to help her.)
5. *Pomozimo* im da nađu svoju sreću. (Let's help them to find their happiness.)